title: One Bedroom Garden Apt facing back of building
posting_body: ['This is a quiet one bedroom apartment with a private patio and garden area off the living room which faces the back of the building -- lined with trees and gardens.', 'The apartment is in a safe neighborhood and a convenient location - one block from Fillmore Street and a block from Japantown.', ' Centrally located and walking distance to two supermarkets, several pharmacies, theatres, many restaurants and shops ...', 'and, just a few minutes drive from downtown.', ' Multiple downtown and cross-town muni lines nearby.', 'The apartment rents for $2350 monthly.', 'Trash and water (hot and cold) are included in rent.', "One-year lease with a security deposit equal to one month's rent, then month to month lease.", 'This is in a rent-controlled building so no surprise rent increases.', '  Large laundry room in building.', 'Please call or text', 'show contact info', 'to see the place.', ' Available for immediate showing and move-in!', 'First come, first serve.', ' No pets allowed.', 'The apartment is located on Webster Street between Bush and Sutter Streets.']
